Oh no! I'm surrounded!

239
00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:25.280
Take aim!

240
00:15:27.530 --> 00:15:28.490
Is this it for me?

241
00:15:28.990 --> 00:15:30.700
On my mark!

242
00:15:30.700 --> 00:15:33.290
Fire!

243
00:15:45.010 --> 00:15:45.590
What?!

244
00:15:46.090 --> 00:15:47.130
What?

245
00:15:48.390 --> 00:15:50.100
What?

246
00:15:53.350 --> 00:15:55.520
What? What?

247
00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:57.810
What?!

248
00:16:01.400 --> 00:16:02.980
It's beautiful!

249
00:16:02.980 --> 00:16:04.070
Wait, no!

250
00:16:04.070 --> 00:16:05.440
What the hell is this?!

251
00:16:05.860 --> 00:16:08.200
Why did a flower come out of the muzzle?!

252
00:16:09.450 --> 00:16:11.700
No, wait...

253
00:16:11.700 --> 00:16:12.870
This is...

254
00:16:16.290 --> 00:16:18.170
one of Dr. Vegapunk's inventions!

255
00:16:22.590 --> 00:16:25.710
It earned him the Mobel Peace Prize!

256
00:16:26.760 --> 00:16:28.840
That's not what I'm asking!

257
00:16:29.470 --> 00:16:31.800
Who did this?!

258
00:16:31.800 --> 00:16:33.010
Koby!

259
00:16:36.430 --> 00:16:38.440
Get over here!

260
00:16:38.440 --> 00:16:39.140
Wait, no!

261
00:16:39.770 --> 00:16:41.360
I didn't mean anythin' weird!

